1. Import the jar ( log4j.jar)
2. Place the Log4j.xml (under the project)---> it holds information of 

	1. where to create a log file (path) (you need to change according to the ur project path)
	2. In which formate you want logs
	3. do you want to append the text or not

3. Intialize the Log4j class

		public static Logger log = Logger.getLogger("CreateLogs");
		BasicConfigurator.configure();
		DOMConfigurator.configure("Log4j.xml");